  "description": "MPM offers a compact, inexpensive refrigerator with a width of only 50 cm, which is suitable for kitchens with limited space and small families. This is a fairly classic model with two chambers, including a fairly spacious freezer located below. The total volume is 176 liters, but inside there is everything necessary for the proper organization of useful space. The refrigerator compartment is equipped with three shelves, a pull-out container for storing vegetables, fruits and herbs, an egg tray and side shelves for placing bottles, sauces, etc. The MPM 182-KB-33 freezer operates at a temperature of -18°C and is capable of freezing almost 3 kg of food per day. It offers three pull-out containers of different sizes, including one large one for larger or oddly shaped products. The refrigerator compartment is defrosted manually thanks to the compressor, which periodically turns off, but the freezer compartment will have to be defrosted manually. A conventional rotary switch is provided to select the appropriate temperature. Another advantage of the model is the ability to reposition the door: you can choose which side the hinges will be located on, taking into account the layout and features of the kitchen.",
